snippet.title: Teaser Gräuel
snippet.description:
WISHLIST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2215790/Gruel/

GRÄUEL is a cooperative horror game (1 to 6 players) where you dive into an endless nightmare. Work as a team to survive the abominations' crises and discover their common history in your nightmares. Preserve your mental health or sink into hell.
